I ask you to join me in saving our freedom and securing our future ‚Äì a future of peace, opportunity, and prosperity for all. When we join together in this effort, I know our best days are still to come. #TheFreedomPlan

Freedom is still our secret weapon. 

If we unlock it, Communist China doesn‚Äôt stand a chance, because nothing is more powerful than the American people. #TheFreedomPlan

The dark days of Bidenomics, with its sky-high inflation and interest rates, struggling families, special-interest handouts, and failed socialism will fade into a distant memory as a hard lesson learned. #TheFreedomPlan
Together, we‚Äôll move forward, into a new era of big ideas, better jobs, and the boundless optimism that lifts up everyone, not just a select few. #TheFreedomPlan

Joe Biden thinks he‚Äôs protecting you from yourself. I trust you. I believe in you. 

A citizen of the United States is the most inspiring and impressive person in the world. You deserve the freedom to prove it once again. #TheFreedomPlan

When we restore Washington to its rightful place, we‚Äôll enter a national renaissance. 

The American people are infinitely creative, and fundamentally trustworthy. #TheFreedomPlan

I‚Äôll force Congress to vote on every rule and regulation, period. 

When politicians have to vote on every price-hiking, job-destroying, family-crushing mandate, you can bet we‚Äôll see a lot fewer rules coming down. #TheFreedomPlan

Under #TheFreedomPlan, we won‚Äôt just have term limits for politicians. 

We will limit bureaucrats too.

No bureaucrat should hold the same position for more than five years.

As Governor of South Carolina, I fought Republicans and Democrats to bring fiscal transparency and discipline to our state. 

They didn‚Äôt like it, but we did it anyway. It‚Äôs time to do the same in Washington. 

When I pick a fight, the people always win! #TheFreedomPlan
If Congress fails to pass a budget, they will fail to get a paycheck. No budget, no pay ‚Äì that‚Äôs a no-brainer. #TheFreedomPlan

In the past 40 years, Congress has passed a pathetic four budgets on time. No more. I‚Äôll fight for zero-based budgeting.

Congress will start from scratch every year, looking at what we have to have rather than what we‚Äôve always spent. #TheFreedomPlan
And when I‚Äôm President, special interests won‚Äôt get a penny in taxpayer bailouts. #TheFreedomPlan

Let‚Äôs put in place a real limit on what Washington can spend. Federal spending should not rise to larger percentages of our economy. If a business kept spending more than it made, it would go broke. 

I refuse to let Congress spend America into bankruptcy. #TheFreedomPlan
I will veto any spending bill that doesn‚Äôt take us back to pre-COVID spending levels. #TheFreedomPlan
Enough is enough. Politicians can‚Äôt spend their way to socialism if they don‚Äôt have the cash. We need to cut up the credit card ‚Äì now. #TheFreedomPlan
We should also eliminate Joe Biden‚Äôs $500 billion in green energy subsidies. No more cash windfalls for China. #TheFreedomPlan
My tax cuts will put thousands of dollars in middle-class families‚Äô pockets. #TheFreedomPlan
We‚Äôll make the small business relief in the 2017 tax cuts permanent. It makes no sense that small businesses got temporary relief, while big businesses got permanent help. #TheFreedomPlan
We‚Äôll cut income taxes for working families. The middle class should have fewer brackets and lower rates. #TheFreedomPlan
Underestimate me, that‚Äôll be fun. https://t.co/e3YbG8J3Dm
We‚Äôll completely eliminate the federal gas and diesel tax. #TheFreedomPlan

My plan starts by giving real relief and financial freedom to middle class Americans. Every middle-class family will get thousands of dollars in tax relief. No one knows how to use your money better than you ‚Äì no one. #TheFreedomPlan
Americans are tired of working for Washington. It‚Äôs time for Washington to start working for us. That‚Äôs why I‚Äôm unveiling #TheFreedomPlan.

Joe Biden is ultimately sending a message to every American: Don‚Äôt bother to dream; don‚Äôt bother to dare. Government‚Äôs got this. We became the greatest country the world has ever seen because we rejected that lie. #TheFreedomPlan
Whether it‚Äôs the big government right or the bigger government left, our leaders are insulting the American people. #TheFreedomPlan

Some Republicans want so-called ‚Äúindustrial policy‚Äù that bails out railroad unions or promotes the misnamed ‚Äústakeholder capitalism.‚Äù  That‚Äôs little more than socialism lite. Republicans used to know that giving DC more control isn‚Äôt the solution‚Äîit‚Äôs the problem. #TheFreedomPlan
Bidenomics is government control of everyone, from job creators to working families. #TheFreedomPlan
As history shows, socialism kills the middle class. #TheFreedomPlan

Joe Biden has created a political subsidy economy. The well-connected are getting wealthier through corporate welfare, while the poor get trapped in regular welfare. That‚Äôs called socialism. #TheFreedomPlan

Look at the grossly misnamed Inflation Reduction Act. Biden‚Äôs signature ‚Äúachievement‚Äù doled out hundreds of billions in blatant corporate welfare, while fueling inflation for everyone else. #TheFreedomPlan
In two-and-a-half years, Joe Biden has done more damage than anyone thought possible. #TheFreedomPlan

I‚Äôm running for President to save our country. We‚Äôll end Joe Biden‚Äôs disastrous slide into socialism. We‚Äôll unlock the power of American freedom. And we‚Äôll move forward, together, into a future of prosperity and peace. #TheFreedomPlan

Joe Biden is building the biggest government in American history. He‚Äôs swapping freedom for socialism. No one is happier than Communist China. 

Few things are more exciting for Xi Jinping than the prospect of four more years of Joe Biden. #TheFreedomPlan

Now is the time to bring out our secret weapon‚Äîfreedom. 

Freedom is the engine behind our great middle class. #TheFreedomPlan

When I announced my candidacy for President, I laid out a vision for a strong and proud America. 

This isn‚Äôt just a slogan. 

Strength and pride are essential to our national survival, especially in the face of Communist China. #TheFreedomPlan

Today, I‚Äôll be delivering my economic vision for a strong and proud America. 

#TheFreedomPlan will revive the middle class, empower families, and strengthen our communities‚Äînot Washington. 

Our secret weapon is freedom and it‚Äôs time to unleash it. https://t.co/CY9JCpl9cJ
